Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会履行义务的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第 10 话 同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半井你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打我们?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快打扫卫生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她让我们快打扫卫生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家长了不得 孩子说的话就是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么卫生 还不快去找找谁是你爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦差点忘了 找也找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈是出去卖的人 谁知道生你这次是卖给谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜可怜她 别继续说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈才不是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来不是啊 不是就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要尽我的义务就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直努力做好该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我仍然觉得 这还是因为我在顾虑妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈是不是应该站街上才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈搭我一起卖 来买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直认为 要好好听话 当个有用的人 不做让人讨厌的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪里不对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了害怕没别的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一所保护的东西 我也必须去保护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不只是他 这是大家一起保护下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想下去都要疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧找点事干 我能干些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都能干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有点太花哨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩子 在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚不在家吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化节的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 我还以为又是找你做裁缝活儿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间做的话推掉不就得了 没必要为挣钱委屈自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你的活儿非得越来越多不可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我喜欢缝纫 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保证营养一定能更变漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是我骄傲的女儿 当然会漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差三件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美子 在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 赶了个前后脚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 带回来的吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做衣服?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 这么董事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡边叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没直接问过你 我妈妈以前真的做过那种事么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么传的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她年轻的时候 因为你妈那时候太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 现在也漂亮 更漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃不吃苹果 很甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡边叔叔 我有件事拜托您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我联系客人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等了很久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以坐下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是半井摩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我叫多多良惣二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是半井 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把车开来 你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半井
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想干涉你们的生活 但你能告诉我这是怎么回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会离开这个城市 能请您别再跟着我了好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事就打我手机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合你口味么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能问一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那么想要钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想说的话没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了证明自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 那我给你钱如何 不用你付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是…为了证明自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的好意我心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您这么做 我会无法原谅自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 只是觉得你真像你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十多年前 你妈妈也这么跟我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您认识我妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你之前就认识了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上 我曾向你妈妈求过婚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是我没有魅力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和美子相遇的时候 我刚进了一家制药公司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等候室看见了一位非常美丽的女士 就过去搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没多久 我就爱上了她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来照顾你和孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的好意我心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想靠自己的力量抚养这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话 我会无法原谅自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美子选择了一条充满艰辛的路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从怀上你之后 她也不再继续那种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也求我帮过忙 但她一定不想依靠男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩子!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来这了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是偶然碰到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把她看成你了 就跟她搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太假了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 摩子 你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人的事 你就少管点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 当妈的应该负首要责任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩子 到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易来一趟 先来喝杯果汁再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是美子的女儿 来杯特制混合果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿? 她就是美子的女儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 到我们这坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩子 你怎么能来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫“这种地方”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 我们可几乎每天晚上都来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板 这可是你管理不力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 您说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美子 快去倒酒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有其母必有其女 太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你 快给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰一下下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要是敢碰我宝贝女儿 那可就不只是钱的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美子 太过分了 竟然以为我是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人弄哭了 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 对不起 不哭不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能动她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想当孩子他爸! 想照顾你俩一辈子!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别说你忘了 我可是认真跟你求婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然想起这个了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 你竟然喜欢美子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年我向她求婚的时候 她说想靠自己的力量扶养孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 我可也跟她求过婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们全都是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…还有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美子姐姐太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 这真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可真丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你明白了吗 摩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这的人都喜欢美子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈是个了不起的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回轮到她哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩子 怎么哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你怎么这么怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪老板多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思不好意思 我又不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作和店里都很重要 但是都没有我的摩子重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就为美子和摩子的未来 干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这家店!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有大家!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧给你瘦的 为了制造美好回忆连觉都不睡了么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是…COSPLAY!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么COSPLAY 那是制服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:18:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,业余水平 做得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这料子 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不够 只做了4套
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是闲着没事就做了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 大家一起穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺合适嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来以为你是个挺闷的人 原来也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事 我们就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉所谓义务 让我们为自己去战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:19:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太怪了 以前都是在自己家所在的城市出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥虫 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是一种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队的直升机也没来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没有平民的话就能放开手脚打了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而对我们有利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会一直挨你的打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不适合近距离格斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要总勉强自己做典范
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果自己负得起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么去随心所欲就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 谢谢您!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来电 公共电话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我是宇白可奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是田中姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可奈?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在方便讲话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我想求您件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请帮我找哥哥的亲生母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要评出世上罪孽最深的人的话 结果一定是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了他们两个 我很高兴献出自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 生命
